description:
The SuperPuTTY Window Manager for putty sessions

SuperPuTTY is a Windows based application which manages putty ssh terminals. Additionally it has a simple scripting language for basic tasks. It additionally support RDP sessions.
- Minor changes Fixes version issue with SuperPuTTY Update Checker Fixes Issues #887, #888, #889
- Children attach improvement by @vityank in #851
- Added RDP Support to Command line by @TzachiSh in #852
New Contributors
- @TzachiSh made their first contribution in #852
Full Changelog: https://github.com/jimradford/superputty/compare/1.4.10...1.5.0.0
